This paper deals with the problem of query-based entailment and inseparability for ALC ontologies, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO). The paper also involves the use of databases (cs.DB) and natural language processing (cs.CL) techniques. Additionally, the paper discusses complexity results, which is a topic related to cryptography and security (cs.CR).
